News.headline: Essex Senior Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Southend
News.page_title: Essex Senior Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Southend
News.URL_keywords: Essex Senior Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Southend
News.short_description: The Daggers have been drawn at home to Southend in the third round of the Essex Senior Cup.
News.description:
The tie will take place on Tuesday 11th October and kick-off at 7:45pm.

Ticket prices:
Adults: £6.00
Concessions/Juniors: £3.00

Tickets for the game will be cash on the turnstiles.
